  "title": "v1.127.0",
  "summary": "What's Changed Use correct param name for setup-bundletool action by @ds-boyce in #11020 WSOD when trying to create account from starter pack on non-default provider by @c960657 in #10970 Replace react-native-compressor video path with native expo-bluesky-video-compress module [APP-2428] by @vineyardbovines in #10954 Always scroll to bottom of chat after se…",
  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Use correct param name for setup-bundletool action by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11020\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11020</a></li>\n<li>WSOD when trying to create account from starter pack on non-default provider by <a href=\"https://github.com/c960657\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@c960657</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10970\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10970</a></li>\n<li>Replace react-native-compressor video path with native expo-bluesky-video-compress module [APP-2428] by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10954\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10954</a></li>\n<li>Always scroll to bottom of chat after sending a message by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10913\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10913</a></li>\n<li>Cull unused files by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11029\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11029</a></li>\n<li>Remove <code>react-native-dotenv</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10706\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10706</a></li>\n<li>Update search input with <code>useAutocomplete</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11023\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11023</a></li>\n<li>Always set <code>allTime</code> to <code>true</code> for search v2 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11033\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11033</a></li>\n<li>Avoid leaking previous messages via replies by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11017\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11017</a></li>\n<li>Use latest fingerprint-native action by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11016\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11016</a></li>\n<li>Bump the actions group with 3 updates by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11021\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11021</a></li>\n<li>Bump actions/checkout from 6.0.3 to 7.0.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11022\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11022</a></li>\n<li>Route iOS notification settings intent into the app by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11003\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11003</a></li>\n<li>Rename root file from <code>js</code> to <code>ts</code>, improve platform splitting by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11012\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11012</a></li>\n<li>Remove actions-up script in favor of Dependabot by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11034\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11034</a></li>\n<li>Fix UI overlap issue where text was rendering over icons by <a href=\"https://github.com/ashish-khankari\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ashish-khankari</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10774\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10774</a></li>\n<li>Add &quot;fingerprint changed&quot; label to PRs with native changes by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10742\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10742</a></li>\n<li>adding focus to the editing block by <a href=\"https://github.com/Zaven477\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Zaven477</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10593\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10593</a></li>\n<li>Only request notification permission once per session by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11004\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11004</a></li>\n<li>Fix hashtag author filter failing for DIDs by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10772\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10772</a></li>\n<li>Fix lint by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11038\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11038</a></li>\n<li>Added Automation label to labeller display names by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11027\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11027</a></li>\n<li>Restore link in Go Live prompt if status record present by <a href=\"https://github.com/LooneyH\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@LooneyH</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10636\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10636</a></li>\n<li>Fix stale display names for lists/feeds in top bar across restarts/devices by <a href=\"https://github.com/RetroSunstar\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@RetroSunstar</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10651\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10651</a></li>\n<li>Fix yaml syntax in pull-request-commit.yml by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11037\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11037</a></li>\n<li>Use RNKC for composer keyboard avoiding view by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10997\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10997</a></li>\n<li>Update advanced search suggestions by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11036\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11036</a></li>\n<li>Reduce Sentry noise from logger transport and expected-failure call sites by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10893\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10893</a></li>\n<li>Bump app version to 1.127.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11040\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11040</a></li>\n<li>Fix blank message list after submit on Android by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11042\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11042</a></li>\n<li>Special-case &#x27;me&#x27; values in search queries by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11043\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11043</a></li>\n<li>[AAv2] Integrate on-device APIs by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/9564\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#9564</a></li>\n<li>Remove potentially intent violating chat settings restriction by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11056\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11056</a></li>\n<li>Fix back button behavior on login/create account screen by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11052\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11052</a></li>\n<li>build: bump Node to 24.18 for June 2026 security releases by <a href=\"https://github.com/amckinley\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@amckinley</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11069\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11069</a></li>\n<li>Clean up media-upload temp files on iOS by <a href=\"https://github.com/so-asano\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@so-asano</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11007\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11007</a></li>\n<li>fix: restore Android native stretchy overscroll on image carousel by <a href=\"https://github.com/Pintu-Jha\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Pintu-Jha</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11072</a></li>\n<li>Add missing l18n wrapper to ‘⚠Invalid Handle’ in handles.ts by <a href=\"https://github.com/smileyhead\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@smileyhead</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11071\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11071</a></li>\n<li>Upgrade pnpm to 11.10.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11075\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11075</a></li>\n<li>fix camera roll gif selection hanging on ios by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11074\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11074</a></li>\n<li>Bump dcarbone/install-jq-action from 3.2.0 to 4.0.1 by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11077\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11077</a></li>\n<li>Bump actions/cache from 5.0.5 to 6.1.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11078\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11078</a></li>\n<li>Bump the actions group with 5 updates by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11076\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11076</a></li>\n<li>Fix zizmor findings in build workflows by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11046\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11046</a></li>\n<li>Automatically resolve hosting provider from handle by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11053\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11053</a></li>\n<li>Clean up feature gate for follow buttons in expanded notifications by <a href=\"https://github.com/abenzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abenzer</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11068\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11068</a></li>\n<li>fix(search): Update advanced search label text (<a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/issues/11049\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11049</a>) by <a href=\"https://github.com/Pintu-Jha\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Pintu-Jha</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11064\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11064</a></li>\n<li>Bump golang.org/x/net from 0.47.0 to 0.55.0 in /bskyweb by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11055\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11055</a></li>\n<li>Force native builds when package.json version changes in OTA deploy by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11061\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11061</a></li>\n<li>Use &#x27;hyphens&#x27; instead of &#x27;dashes&#x27; in error string by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11050\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11050</a></li>\n<li>fix web video preview error aborting upload by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11079\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11079</a></li>\n<li>Use Sift for username suggestions during signup by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11051\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11051</a></li>\n<li>Bump github.com/jackc/pgx/v5 from 5.5.0 to 5.9.2 in /bskyweb by <a href=\"https://github.com/dependabot\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@dependabot</a>[bot] in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10463\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10463</a></li>\n<li>Fix back swipe opening the drawer after a cold-start deep link by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11065\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11065</a></li>\n<li>v1.127.0 release by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11087\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11087</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>New Contributors</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ashish-khankari\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ashish-khankari</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10774\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10774</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/LooneyH\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@LooneyH</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10636\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10636</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/so-asano\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@so-asano</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11007\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11007</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Pintu-Jha\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@Pintu-Jha</a> made their first contribution in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/11072\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#11072</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/compare/1.126.0...1.127.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.126.0...1.127.0</a></p>",
